sentences: Juan Diego Calleros Ramos (born 19 April 1962) is a Mexican musician.
Along with Fher Olvera and his brothers Ulises and Abraham, Juan was part of Sombrero Verde (1978–1985) which, in 1986, transformed to Maná.
